{"tid":2309857,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警員調查汽油彈案欲解鎖手機 疑推被告上半身出窗外威脅掟落樓","createTime":"2020-12-03T00:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T10:47:01.000Z","uid":239336,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e002859b96d1b94af79d6ff83f0b1723743ec8a4","tid":2309857,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T00:30:56.000Z","msg":"去年10月1日警方在銅鑼灣一個單位內搜出白電油及布條等物品，拘捕六名男女，控以串謀縱火罪，惟控方開審前夕突然改控串謀暴動罪。案件今續審，辯方指有警員當時為求得到被告的手機密碼，開啟窗戶推被告上半身出窗，警告謂：「快啲講！再唔講掟你落樓！」警員又疑捉住其中一名女被告到窗邊並對她說：「生得好眉好貌，點解要做呢啲嘢？」「你今次死梗，你唔死都冇用，不如跳出去。」<br />\n<br />\n辯方盤問鄧時指，警方持爆破工具入屋，向屋內各被告說「再郁打爆你個頭」；又指事發時首被告背囊內原本只有銀包，是鄧將防毒面具、護目鏡、手袖、紅色燈及綠色繩放入背囊內；鄧否認。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又指，鄧帶首被告入洗手間，要求首被告交出手機密碼，又試過捉住首被告的手按在其手機，企圖要首被告解鎖。惟首被告一直拒絕交出密碼，鄧不耐煩謂：「快啲講！再唔講掟你落樓！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/65YUZKQNGVEQJBUPCJN22SB6VY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0Se0MGHAObQ9Pyc306Hz5iu8cOw6NdWxKsWN6f9G-bscEiMPdZ4Z_66Eo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2F65YUZKQNGVEQJBUPCJN22SB6VY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0Se0MGHAObQ9Pyc306Hz5iu8cOw6NdWxKsWN6f9G-bscEiMPdZ4Z_66Eo&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOXB8Xc4SSRTU1%2BC3UxNwN9M%3D&h=a801f87f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2F65YUZKQNGVEQJBUPCJN22SB6VY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0Se0MGHAObQ9Pyc306Hz5iu8cOw6NdWxKsWN6f9G-bscEiMPdZ4Z_66Eo&h=882c71c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/65YUZKQNGVEQJBUPCJN22SB6VY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0Se0MGHAObQ9Pyc306Hz5i